# AWS Lambda Function

## Overview

This Lambda function processes banking application requests for the Secure Financial Data Management System.

The function supports three main workflows:

- KYC workflow initiation
- Transaction record creation
- Customer statement generation

## Supported Actions

### KYC

Starts an AWS Step Functions workflow for customer verification.

### Transaction

Creates a transaction record and stores it in Amazon DynamoDB.

### Statement

Queries customer transaction records, generates a statement, and stores it in Amazon S3.

## AWS Services Used

- AWS Lambda
- Amazon DynamoDB
- Amazon S3
- AWS Step Functions
- Amazon CloudWatch
- AWS IAM
- AWS KMS

